{
  "stem": "7093.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But this teacher treated me so badly that eventually, my father-- after the third year, my father made a petition to try and get him-- that he should be pensioned off and that he wasn't suitable to deal with small children.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And eventually, the other people who said they would sign, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They opted out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so my father took me out and put me into-- for the fourth year, put me into a state school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because I was so-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I-- because he so maltreated me, I just couldn't learn at all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And therefore, if I had bad marks, since we had numerous classes in the-- in the higher schools, I couldn't have got into a-- a proper higher school if with my marks, with my low marks.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And therefore, he put me into another school, a state school where among 600 children I was only Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was a rather tough year to go through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But actually, it wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I got extremely good marks in that school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I did-- I was one of the best in the class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that helped me then to get into a sort of grammar school, a girls' lyceum, which was sort of girls grammar school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I was there for five years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "When I was 13, we were-- no, just a minute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That was-- anyway, 1938 the Germans walked into Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we-- the town-- we lived on the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And from the-- at the-- because we were in the Austrian border and we had family in Vienna, they brought over-- my father had quite a few clients, patients, in-- over the border.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the-- the town was such that there was a mountain in between Austria and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
